		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Rare (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p><em>This robe is adorned with eyelike patterns that dart and blink.</em></p><p><em>A magic item like this grants a bonus to checks where relevant and counts as magical for overcoming effects.</em></p><p><strong>Buff</strong></p><ul><li><p>You have Advantage on &amp;reference[Perception] checks that rely on sight.</p></li><li><p>You have &amp;reference[Darkvision] and &amp;reference[Truesight], both with a range of 120 feet.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Drawbacks</strong></p><ul><li><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.e4MmHYtpD4jFrRuH]{Light}</em> cast on the robe or <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.jdFMmZrR5TJegYvD]{Daylight}</em> cast within 5 feet gives you the &amp;Reference[Blinded] condition for 1 minute.</p></li><li><p>At the end of each of your turns, make a Constitution save (DC 11 vs <em>Light</em>, DC 15 vs <em>Daylight</em>) to end the condition on a success.</p></li></ul>",
